Awesome performance by Dean Cain as Laci Peterson's murdering husband. Sad but true story of a missing pregnant wife and a cheating husband that could do the unthinkable, 5 stars all the way. Highly recommended!
Nothing wrong with the film itself, got here on time, the movie work fine, I just didn't like the story much.
